readme: Improve this doc # File Path ``` $ ionic cordova plugin add cordova-plugin-filepath $ npm install --save @ionic-native/file-path ``` ## [Usage Documentation](https://ionicframework.com/docs/native/file-path/) Plugin Repo: [https://github.com/hiddentao/cordova-plugin-filepath](https://github.com/hiddentao/cordova-plugin-filepath) This plugin allows you to resolve the native filesystem path for Android content URIs and is based on code in the aFileChooser library. ## Supported platforms - Android
